219
00:22:00,840 --> 00:22:02,850
Podívejte co dělat?

220
00:22:09,450 --> 00:22:13,220
Hey!

221
00:22:13,290 --> 00:22:16,320
Ty losy!

222
00:22:19,020 --> 00:22:23,970
♫ <i>Hádej, kam tě cesta zavede</i> ♫

223
00:22:24,010 --> 00:22:29,910
