512
00:44:53,700 --> 00:44:56,890
Ahoj, Yan Li Zheng!

513
00:44:58,820 --> 00:45:00,780
Tvůj pokoj?

514
00:45:00,780 --> 00:45:03,040
Xiao Yu ti to neřekl?

515
00:45:03,040 --> 00:45:08,180
